{"tid":754645,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=To Hell? 今年上半年爆5宗升降機意外　1人身亡","createTime":"2018-07-24T14:33:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T06:10:29.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"557986855e3de86add0379b884b6f14d3788b2c4","tid":754645,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T14:33:24.000Z","msg":"近年升降機意外頻生，機電工程署公布，今年上半年便有5宗升降機意外，去年全年則有8宗。而在去年7月至今年6月，機電署發給註冊升降機承辦商警告信共有11宗。<br />\n<br />\n今年上半年的5宗意外，首宗發生於1月25日，旺角亞皆老街水務署升降機機箱平層故障引致乘客受傷，升降機承建商為其士(香港)有限公司。另一宗在3月22日發生，西貢街市升降機電器部件故障，引致乘客受傷，承建商為星瑪電梯(香港)有限公司。3月30日在粉嶺華明邨耀明樓亦發生意外，當時升降機控制系統故障，導致乘客受傷，承建商為東哲電梯工程有限公司。荃灣海灣花園第2座的升降機，4月8日因制動系統失效引致乘客受傷，承建商為通力電梯(香港)有限公司；上水名都巴黎閣的升降機，5月11日亦因制動系統失效，引致乘客死亡，承建商為耀天工程有限公司。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180724/bkn-20180724171457222-0724_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180724%2Fbkn-20180724171457222-0724_00822_001.html&d=6AKR81sUGUeq1ap08EE1cuPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=a601ae3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180724/bkn-20180724171457222-0724_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"efa04b92970b6fe9f0845430795117550f4d297a","tid":754645,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T14:35:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://ifanzine.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Journey-To-Hell-Featured.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fifanzine.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F03%2FJourney-To-Hell-Featured.jpg&h=d479b682&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d588ec39b227d20e83adda39077829445274a8b6","tid":754645,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T06:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/140135_19139db86472d308a18e2d4585ae929e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F140135_19139db86472d308a